{"tid":1613955,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"[檢討]落荒而逃前須知","createTime":"2019-10-02T16:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T03:11:39.000Z","uid":19793,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"68a420de9740e02ae90905d815c390357c4f6c9e","tid":1613955,"uid":19793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:12:52.000Z","msg":"國殤日夢見十幾隻狗趕幾百人<br />\n開頭要人嘅時候前線手足又跪又屌，<br />\n後面依然神態自若散步咁行。<br />\n後尾勉強聚到少少人，放幾粒煙之後，<br />\n後排幾百人部份full gear嘅跑走哂去<br />\n唔好話聞到連見都未必見到煙嘅位置。<br />\n最後前線無奈只可以跟住撤，<br />\n走嘅時候可以聽到見到佢地有幾嬲幾失望。<br />\n<br />\n講呢啲野唔係要屌大家，唔係要分化<br />\n只係想提醒大家跑走之前留意以下幾點，<br />\n因為你不必要嘅恐慌帶走嘅唔只係你一個，而係可能幾百個跟住你跑走嘅人。<br />\n少一個真係好少。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/87FDQMk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F87FDQMk.jpg&h=fa7ec89b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4260d8f15ebfdd71c246962a30af2d2abb86388e","tid":1613955,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:13:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6ec8cc08a3b898ceb2a9433b38e3711621dcacb","tid":1613955,"uid":64092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e94ddef08be404260136fffa014e15e8b72644","tid":1613955,"uid":19793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef0fb516e8b3402a0d86925806ef404a2e942e2","tid":1613955,"uid":19793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:48:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b51b8d3ebfd7781e49d77b7c3840b1030696128","tid":1613955,"uid":232671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:49:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56c34e8ef9864d7e5ad3fa13ce2e4f9b0d545d0c","tid":1613955,"uid":48165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"rep